ACR

1. Managed ,private docker registry.
2. Create and maintain azure container registries to store and manage our private docker container images.
3. With acr we can simplfy container lifecycle management.
4. Geo-replication to efficiently manage a single registry across multiple regions.
5. Automate conatainer building and patching inclusin base image update and task scheduling.
6. Integrated security with Azure ad authentication, RBAC and docker container trust and virtual netwok integrations.


